#: ../../../doc/en/how-to/output.rst:267
msgid ""
"Those were examples of how verbosity affects normal test session output, but "
"verbosity also is used in other situations, for example you are shown even "
"fixtures that start with ``_`` if you use ``pytest --fixtures -v``."
